2:T6c8,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Drift better than Kayako?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Drift scores 7.0 overall while Kayako scores 5.0. Drift is best for B2B sales teams and demand generation, while Kayako excels for mid-size businesses and support teams."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Drift or Kayako?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Drift starts at Custom and Kayako starts at $39/agent/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Drift to Kayako?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Drift and Kayako support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Drift vs Kayako?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Drift holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10. Kayako has an overall rating of 5/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Drift for excellent for b2b lead qualification and Kayako for good customer journey visualization."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Drift or Kayako?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Drift for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Kayako remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize good customer journey visualization. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"contai